---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Soumyo Dey">
  <main class="py-12">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">About Me</h1>

    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
        Hi! I'm Soumyo Dey, a software developer and food enthusiast who combines my passion for
        technology with my love for exploring world cuisines, especially noodles.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold">My Journey</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        With over 5 years of experience in full-stack development, I've worked with startups and
        established companies alike. My technical expertise includes JavaScript/TypeScript, React,
        Node.js, and Python. Currently, I work remotely, which allows me to pursue my other passion:
        traveling the world and discovering unique food experiences.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold">What I Do</h2>
      <ul class="mb-6 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
        <li>Develop web applications using modern technologies</li>
        <li>Write about my travel and food experiences</li>
        <li>Create content about developer lifestyle and remote work</li>
        <li>Contribute to open-source projects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold">Current Focus</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I'm currently focused on building tools that help digital nomads and remote workers find the
        best places to work and eat around the world. When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring
        local food markets or trying out new recipes in my temporary kitchen.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and food enthusiasts. Feel free
        to reach out to me on social media or via email.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@johndoe.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-purple-600 px-4 py-2 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-purple-700"
        >
          Email Me
        </a>
        <a
          href="/resume"
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-purple-600 px-4 py-2 text-base font-medium text-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-50 dark:hover:bg-purple-900"
        >
          View Resume
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
